title._content: View of boulder photographed during second Apollo 17 EVA

description._content: Collection: NASA Johnson Space Center Collection Title: View of boulder photographed during second Apollo 17 EVA Description: View of boulder at Station 2 (Amundsen Crater) photographed during second Apollo 17 extrvehicular activity (EVA-2). The earth can be seen directly above the boulder in the lunar sky.
